         <ab>Y28.2 (mss. 40, 88, 400, 410 (sec. m.), 2030, 2101, 2106):</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            frāxgām pad ǰām nihišn ō ī barsom barišn pad abārīg hamgōnag kunišn yānīm bun hāwan škāftan</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            "He has to put the <em>frāxgām</em> on the vessel and (then) to bring it to the <em>barsom</em>. At the other (beginnings of <em>hād</em>) he has to do in the same way. 
            Beginning of the Yānīm. He should hit the <em>hāwan</em>."</ab>
      </Nerangs>
